		<title>冠心病病人吃什么水果好（冠心病最“怕”这3类水果）</title>
		<link>https://www.huacao77.com/11614.html</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[广少, 腹肌之广]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 08:39:12 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[果蔬知识]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[冠心病]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[患者]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[死亡率]]></category>
